License: UNKNOWN
Description: # PyPgm
        
        This package is for reading portable greymap files.
        
        Functionality still to be added for writing pgm files.
        
        # Installation
        
        ```cmd
        pip install pgm_reader
        ```
        
        # Usage
        
        ```python
        from pgm_reader import Reader
        
        f = 'pgm_file.pgm'
        reader = Reader()
        image = reader.read_pgm(f)
        width = reader.width
        ```
